title: Kipp's Alehouse
typeOfFood: International, Western, Beer/Wine, British, Moroccan, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Venue with live music. The food that is made-in-house is vegan and includes a Moroccan couscous with hummus and carrot salad and chermoula or harissa; a Thai quinoa with carrot salad, soy cashews and sweet chili sauce served hot or cold; chocolate brownies and date slices. Also has info on which beers and ciders are vegan. Food that is brought in and not prepared onsite are non-veg.
